\section secWhatIsIt What is UG4?

<strong>UG4</strong> is a simulation framework, targetted at the solution of 
differential equations on unstructured hybrid grids on massive parallel systems 
in 1, 2 and 3 dimensions.
<strong>UG4</strong> is written in C++, striving for a flexible, yet fast and 
robust simulation environment.


